title: Chiclets ETC: Episode 1
description:
On Episode 1 of Chiclets ETC, hosts Matt Murley and Colby Armstrong are joined by Paul Bissonnette and Ryan Whitney to talk all things Spittin' Chiclets, Beer League, Dad life and TONS more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
